The Diseases of Animals (Approved Disinfectants) (Amendment) (No. 3) Order 1991
entry.summary: This Order further amends the Diseases of Animals (Approved Disinfectants) Order 1978 by adding to the list of approved disinfectants in that Order those newly approved disinfectants which are mentioned in Schedule 1 to this Order (article 3(1)) and by deleting from that list the disinfectants mentioned in Schedule 2 (article 3(2)). The disinfectants deleted may, however, continue to be used as approved disinfectants until 31st December 1991 (article 3(3) and (4)).

entry.title: The Land Registration Fees Order 1991
entry.summary: The Order, which, as from 1st November 1991, supersedes the Land Registration Fees (No. 2) Order 1990 (“the 1990 order”), revises the land registration fee scales and makes certain other changes.

entry.title: The Statistics (Confidentiality) (Northern Ireland) Order 1991
